language ESSENCE 2.4.0

given n : int
letting N be domain int(0..n-1)
given M : function (total) (N,N) --> int
given J : function (total) (N,N) --> int

find C : function (total) (N,N) --> int(0..1)

such that 

forAll i,j:N. ((i = j) /\ (C((i,j)) = 0)) \/ 
              (!(M((i,j)) = i) /\ (C((i,j)) = 0)) \/
              ((M((i,j)) = i) /\ C((i,j)) = 0) /\ (exists k:N. ((M((j,k)) = k) /\ (M((k,i)) = i) /\ !(k = i) /\ !(j = k) )) \/
              (C((i,j)) = 1)
